  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Last updated: June 28, 2026</strong></p>
  <p>AutoPost ("we", "our", "the app") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we handle information.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>This app does not collect, store, or share any personal data from users. The only data accessed is your TikTok account credentials (via OAuth), used solely to post content on your behalf.</p>

  <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>Your TikTok OAuth access token is used exclusively to publish content to your own TikTok account. It is never shared with third parties.</p>

  <h2>Data Storage</h2>
  <p>No personal data is stored on any external server. All credentials are stored locally on your own device.</p>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>This app interacts with the TikTok API. Please refer to <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank">TikTok's Privacy Policy</a> for information on how TikTok handles your data.</p>

